expenditures.Purpose: Reimbursement for 1-year Zoom membership for on-line meetings.
expenditures.Expenditure Paid Communications Quantity: We anticipate a minimum of 10 Central Committee meetings as well as sub-committee meetings and opportunities to have personal, virtual conversations with candidates, especially during the pandemic crisis.
expenditures.Expenditure Paid Communications Subject: We opted to pay the annual membership because it saved us money over the monthly fee of $14.99.  Zoom meetings allow people from throughout the county to attend without having to drive long distances, especially in winter.
